Bug ID: BUG-001  
Title: Login fails when email contains leading/trailing spaces  

Environment:
Chrome browser (Version XX), macOS  

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Navigate to login page  
2. Enter email: "  testuser@gmail.com  "  
3. Enter password: Password123  
4. Click "Login"  

Expected Result:
System trims whitespace and logs user in successfully  

Actual Result:
Login fails and displays "Invalid email or password"  

Severity:
Medium  

Priority:
Medium  

Bug ID: BUG-002  
Title: No validation message displayed for empty email field  

Environment:
Chrome browser, Windows 11  

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Navigate to login page  
2. Leave email field empty  
3. Enter password: Password123  
4. Click "Login"  

Expected Result:
Validation error message should appear indicating email is required  

Actual Result:
No error message is displayed and login attempt proceeds  

Severity:
High  

Priority:
High  

