Bug ID: BUG-003  
Title: Application crashes when extremely long email is entered  

Environment:
Chrome browser, macOS  

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Navigate to login page  
2. Enter email with 250+ characters  
3. Enter password: Password123  
4. Click "Login"  

Expected Result:
System should reject input with validation message  

Actual Result:
Page freezes and becomes unresponsive  

Severity:
Critical  

Priority:
High  

